com.google.javascript.jscomp.newtypes

Class FunctionTypeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.javascript.jscomp.newtypes.FunctionTypeBuilder

  • public final class FunctionTypeBuilder
extends Object
    A builder for FunctionType and DeclaredFunctionType. The builder is called during both JSDoc parsing and type inference, and these parts use different warning systems, so expect the context to handle the exception appropriately.
    Author:
    blickly@google.com (Ben Lickly), dimvar@google.com (Dimitris Vardoulakis)
